author: Quinten Spaete

text:
Ordered item that ended up being out of stock, had to wait a bit for a new supply to be manufactured. But the staff kept me up to date along the way and were pleasant to work with.
I never write reviews, so this shows how well everything worked out.
Peace bruh.
